On Earth, we call this 'looking at the bigger picture'.<br>
<br>
'4) Let me restate that, why would any chanter want to go to ntov and die five or ten times to get a bunch of melees more crap.'<br>
<br>
- See above. It helps the entire guild, it helps you.<br>
<br>
'5) I'm a firm believer in the fact that other then a couple of flowing thought items, that I really don't need any more gear when my resists are 100 and cha/int is over 225. Its not like casters get that many cool looking robes.'<br>
<br>
- The only thing I can say about this is... why are you moaning about not getting loot if you don't want loot? And yes, we get cool looking robes. *stares blankly*<br>
<br>
